@chapter Suggestions

@c --------------------
@section Can Dinotrace directly read VCD+/VPD format files?

Nope, sorry.  VCD+ is a proprietary format, and the reading code must be
licensed for a fee before being used.  This is obviously not possible with
the distribution philosophy of Dinotrace.

You can however convert VCD+ files on the fly using vpd2vcd.  See the
documentation for details.

